    <!-- ===================== ABSTRACT ====================== -->

    <abstract>

      <para> A supplement to the classic rabbit epic <citetitle>Watership Down</citetitle> by the late
          <personname>Richard Adams</personname>. It includes a full index, a glossary, and chapter
        summaries.</para>
      <para><citetitle>Watership Down</citetitle> is the best book in the whole world. It was the basis for a smash hit 1978 <link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Watership_Down_%28film%29">film</link> of the same name. I'm still recovering from that experience, as we all are.</para>
      <para><citetitle>Watership Down</citetitle> is &#169; <personname>Richard Adams</personname>.</para>
      <para>Comments welcome: <email>johngtait@gmail.com</email>. Please say hello if you like this.</para>
      <note><para>This is a work in progress. I'm going really slow, one chapter at a time.</para></note>
    </abstract>


